Summary: I saw a metallic disk over the shoulder of a realestate agent in the distance in Mount Washington,KY on 9-5-05
divs: Sighting Details9-5-05 I had an appointment to see a realestate agent at 10:30AM in the morning I met the agent and looked at a patio home. In leaving I was talking to the realestate agent in the parking lot when I saw over her shoulder a metallic sliver the sun was reflecting off of it,this object was not moving,the sky was a caribean blue that day no clouds.Ilooked back over at the realestate agent not to be rude and when I looked back this time the object was tilted a metallic disk with a bump in the middle of it at this point fear came over me I don't know why I looked at it for a few seconds and then looked back at the realestate agent and then looked back it was gone.The time seeing this object from beginning to end was about 20 to 25 seconds in the direction of I-65.What it was I don't Know.
